  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for bonus collectibles and extra hidden object challenges! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make matches, find details, memory, montage, and swap tiles, too! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through the game in any order you want!</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>Collector's Edition</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24 extra bonus levels! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wallpapers and soundtrack also included!</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Just Find It 2, prepare to be immersed in a thought-provoking collection of new games! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428320/extras/07435ad12fe1dae676a6348100a3b977.poster.avif?t=1729638968\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428320/extras/07435ad12fe1dae676a6348100a3b977.webm?t=1729638968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428320/extras/07435ad12fe1dae676a6348100a3b977.mp4?t=1729638968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find all the differences, make matches, play memory games, and challenging puzzles for unexpected surprises that will keep you engaged throughout your adventure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428320/extras/d3155a629b0ef297c2940f55c8c5f11b.poster.avif?t=1729638968\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428320/extras/d3155a629b0ef297c2940f55c8c5f11b.webm?t=1729638